Template: hsn2/broker
Type: string
Default: localhost
Description: Broker hostname or ip
 Part of HSN2 common service configuration.

Template: hsn2/datastore
Type: string
Default: localhost:8080
Description: Datastore hostname or ip and port
 Part of HSN2 common service configuration.

Template: hsn2/maxthreads
Type: string
Default: 5
Description: Maximum number of threads
 The maximum number of threads to start per service.
 Part of HSN2 common service configuration.
